dct_title_s: Plan der Stadt Jena und ihrer nächsten Umgebung
dct_description_sm: Map of Jena and environs in the German state of Thuringia. Relief shown by contours. "Ausgabe für die Festgäste des Universitäts-Jubiläums 1908." Includes northern and western profiles. Indexed for streets and points of interest.
